Sure, the last four are five six seven eight.

Thank you for the information, Alex. I'll pull up your billing records now to see what's going on.

Thanks for your help, Jamie.

You're welcome, Alex. Thank you for your patience and for calling West Barnstable Horse Hides. Have a great day!
